    <h1>Dealers - Module</h1>
        <p>The dealers module is built off of the user accounts inside Quarx. It enables the users to maintain a listing of Territory Managers and Dealers. Within it you can set access for dealers and TMs allowing them to update thier profiles. TMs are able to update their dealer profiles and add, enable, disable them etc.</p>
